==Honours==
With the French national team:
*[[FIFA]] [[FIFA World Cup|World Cup]]
**Appearances: 1998, 2002, 2006
**Winner: 1998
**Runner-Up: 2006
*[[European Football Championship|European Championship]]
**Winner: 2000
**Appearances: 2000, 2004
*[[Confederations Cup]]: 2003

With [[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]]:
*[[Ligue 1]]: 1996-97
*[[French Super Cup]]: 1997

With [[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]:
*[[FA Premier League]]: 2001-02, 2003-04
*[[FA Cup]]: 2002, 2003, 2005
*[[FA Community Shield]]: 2002, 2004
*[[UEFA Champions League]] Runner Up : 2006
*[[UEFA Cup]] Runner Up : 2000
Personal Honours:
*[[European Golden Boot]]: 2004, 2005
*[[FA Premier League#Top scorers|FA Premier League Top Scorer]]: 2001-02, 2003-04, 2004-05, 2005-06
*[[Onze d'Or]]: 2003, 2006
*[[PFA Players' Player of the Year]]: 2002-03, 2003-04
*[[Football Writers' Association Footballer of the Year|FWA Footballer Of The Year]]: 2002-03, 2003-04, 2005-06
*[[FIFPro#World XI|World XI]] Striker: 2006

